    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>LEAD: A water truck crashed into a crowd of pedestrians and street vendors here Friday night, killing at least 17 people and injuring five others, witnesses said. The accident occurred in the densely populated Post Marchand slum neighborhood.</p>
